{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_o8mqvbukiwjyf1eu6qay","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"361658117","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/work/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation using a Map-based storage.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates and returns a new cache instance with `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear` methods.\n\n**Return type:** Object\n\n**Example:**\n\n```javascript\nimport { createCache } from './cache.mjs'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves the value associated with the given key from the cache.\n\n**Parameters:**\n\n- `key` - The cache key to look up\n\n**Returns:** The cached value for the key, or `undefined` if not found.\n\n**Example:**\n\n```javascript\ncache.set('foo', 'bar')\ncache.get('foo') // 'bar'\ncache.get('missing') // undefined\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache under the specified key.\n\n**Parameters:**\n\n- `key` - The cache key to use\n- `value` - The value to store\n\n**Returns:** The stored value.\n\n**Example:**\n\n```javascript\ncache.set('foo', 'bar') // 'bar'\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves the entry for the specified key from the cache.\n\n**Parameters:**\n\n- `key` - The cache key to delete\n\n**Returns:** `true` if the key existed and was deleted, `false` otherwise.\n\n**Example:**\n\n```javascript\ncache.delete('foo') // true\ncache.delete('missing') // false\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n**Returns:** `undefined`\n\n**Example:**\n\n```javascript\ncache.clear()\n```\n\n---\n\n**Source:** `bench-targets/docs/src/cache.mjs`\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5216,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":5116},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"59e57a0c-6661-40da-a323-f093de6010b6","uuid":"a7105156-a42d-4fc1-953e-79ca4abfa7af","timestamp":"2026-07-23T01:45:53.847Z"}
